Read-only audit complete. I did not modify files. The checkout was already dirty in root and in `pipeline/`; I treated that as pre-existing and only read files.

**Bottom Line**
`DM_obs` is not currently citable. The root `CONTEXT.md` explicitly revokes DM_obs for all 12 because current tables do not distinguish CHIME-side from DSA-side measurements, do not quantify agreement, and do not document how each was obtained (`CONTEXT.md:28-34`, `CONTEXT.md:48-54`). The revalidation plan says the desired end state is a per-burst, per-telescope DM_obs provenance table with value, error, method, producing artifact, and CHIME-DSA agreement (`docs/rse/specs/plan/plan-trust-reset-revalidation.md:103-106`).

